metadata.name: Freeman of the Armed Services
metadata.description: From the ashes of Steve Dowling's "Garth" comes?"FREEMAN of the Armed Services," Huw-J-'s critically acclaimed web comic that originally re-launched the adventures of the Daily Mirror syndicate's action and adventure hero. Incorporating the story arcs "Gold of Ragnarock" and "King of New York," both which hearken back to the good old days where the spirit of adventure and good old-fashioned action reigned supreme. A true British hero!
